<s> subtag and a (possibly empty) series of subsequent subtags.  </s>
<s> The syntax of this tag in ABNF [RFC 2234] is: Language-Tag = Primary-subtag *( "-" Subtag ) Primary-subtag = 1*8ALPHA Subtag = 1*8(ALPHA / DIGIT)  </s>
<s> The productions ALPHA and DIGIT are imported from RFC 2234; they  </s>
<s> denote respectively the characters A to Z in upper or lower case and  </s>
<s> the digits from 0 to 9. The character "-" is HYPHEN-MINUS (ABNF:  </s>
<s> %x2D).  </s>
